航不懂去驚怕<br />\n荊荊棘棘通通斬去不必多看它<br />\n浮浮沉沉昨日人群雖不說一話<br />\n不想清楚分析太多真心抑意假<br />\n<br />\n但有一個夢 不會死 記著吧<br />\n無論雨怎麼打 自由仍是會開花<br />\n但有一個夢 不會死 記著吧<br />\n來自你我的心 記著吧<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1YeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=6fa04b99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n<br />\n忘不了的 留下了不死意識<br />\n深深相信始終會變真某年某夕<br />\n如此訊息 仍賴你跟我全力<br />\n加一把勁 將這理想繼續在尋覓<br />\n<br />\n悠悠長長繼續前航不懂去驚怕<br />\n荊荊棘棘通通斬去不必多看它<br />\n浮浮沉沉昨日人群雖不說一話<br />\n不想清楚分析太多真心抑意假<br />\n<br />\n但有一個夢 不會死 記著吧<br />\n無論雨怎麼打 自由仍是會開花<br />\n但有一個夢 不會死 記著吧<br />\n來自你我的心 記著吧"},{"pid":"9db8c0c1440e87c4b397a2750c7256ce55a91c61","tid":1132403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"民陣"},{"pid":"f84ee52c65c815669c5d88968e4f8afd4bad7597","tid":1132403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9db8c0c1440e87c4b397a2750c7256ce55a91c61","tid":1132403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"民陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"6月9日 星期日<br />\n反送中遊行<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道至立法會<br />\n1430 集合， 1500 出發"},{"pid":"036ce3e574525aab5b4c65cbbc9c30a21e7c91be","tid":1132403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"冇錯， 岑子杰講得啱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dba8c942a17edfe4822ebc30b28f7f536816d2e","tid":1132403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"